# mapping.db defines raw-bank id -> module id mapping for evio_parser.
# Each non-comment row is: module bank
# At runtime, evio_parser matches the raw EVIO bank id (bank column)
# and assigns it to the corresponding module id (module column).
# module  bank
  250    250
  250    3
  9250   9250
  9001   9001
  3561   3561
  3561   10
  9      9
